花农的烦恼：情人节到了，百余亩上市鲜花却没卖出去。
Flower farmers worry: Valentine's Day has arrived, more than 100 acres of flowers have not been sold.
蔡越坤2020-02-14 15:59。
Cai Yuekun 2020-02-14 15: 59.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 蔡越坤 “100多亩已经上市的鲜花基本没卖出去，‘全军覆没’。
"The economic observation network reporter Cai Yakun" more than 100 mu has been listed flowers have not been sold, 'the whole army lost.
”2月14日，李叔难过地告诉经济观察网记者。
On February 14, Uncle Li sadly told reporters at the Economic Watch.
。
.
李叔，全名叫李海岗，是云南慕妍花卉种植有限公司的负责人。
Uncle Li, whose full name is Li Haigang, is the head of Yunnan Muyan Flower Cultivation Co. Ltd.
李叔说，公司的董事长王都带领大家一起创业，他们共计承包了500多亩地种植鲜花。
Uncle Li said Wang, the company's chairman, is leading everyone to start a business. They have contracted more than 500 mu of land to grow flowers.
。
.
每年的情人节前夕，是李叔和公司同事最忙碌的时候，然而今年情人节前夕，李叔却与同事们在几百亩花地里发愁。
While Uncle Li and his co-workers are busiest on Valentine's Day each year, he and his colleagues worry about hundreds of acres of flowers on Valentine's Day.
。
.
李叔和他的花棚。
Uncle Li and his shed.
李叔说，公司所承包的地位于楚雄彝族自治州苍岭镇，平常售卖鲜花都是运送到昆明的鲜花交易市场。
Li said the company's contracted land is located in Cangling Township, Chuxiong Yi Autonomous Prefecture, where flowers are usually sold to the Kunming flower market.
然而今年，大多鲜花消费者都在家里，也无购买鲜花需求。
This year, however, most flower consumers are at home, and there is no demand for flowers.
此外，鲜花种植地出村的路也被封了，即使可以出村，也面临无法再回村的局面。
In addition, the roads leading out of the village where the flowers were grown were blocked, and even if they were able to leave the village, they would not be able to return to it.
此外，物流也无法及时配送。
Moreover, logistics cannot be delivered in time.
。
.
2月14日这一周，李叔公司种植的100多亩鲜花已经上市，但受当地交通管制、物流配送不及时等影响，鲜花很难销售。
During the week of Feb. 14, more than 100 acres of flowers grown by Uncle Li have been on the market, but flowers are hard to sell because of local traffic control and slow distribution.
最后，他们只能将鲜花一车车倒掉，预计公司损失600万左右。
In the end, they were able to dump only a truckload of flowers, costing the company about 6 million dollars.
。
.
此前的2月12日，李叔在抖音（抖音昵称“花农李叔”）拍了倒掉鲜花的短视频，并配了文字：“当鲜花倒入垃圾堆里的一刹那，花农麻木了。
Earlier, on Feb. 12, Uncle Li filmed a short video of the flowers being poured out, with the words, "When the flowers are poured into the garbage, the growers are numb.
”。
"
100多亩鲜花不仅颗粒无收，李叔所在的公司面临着成本支出的压力。
More than 100 acres of flowers have been lost. Uncle Li's company is under pressure to pay its bills.
。
.
李叔说，500多亩鲜花的成本包括：土地承包费用，一亩2000元；共计200多个工人，目前100多个仍然在上班，每个工人工资每个月平均2500-3000元；农药化肥，一亩地在13000-15000元。
The cost of more than 500 mu of flowers includes land-contracting costs of 2,000 yuan a acre, more than 100 workers are still at work, with an average monthly wage of 2,500 to 3,000 yuan per worker, and 13,000 to 15,000 yuan for pesticide fertilizer.
此外，还不包括工人吃住、鲜花种植大棚的损耗，因为鲜花种植大棚需要3-4年换一次薄膜。
In addition, it does not take into account the loss of food and shelter for workers and the loss of greenhouses where flowers are grown, which takes three to four years to change.
。
.
李叔粗略统计，一个月下来，500多亩鲜花种植地成本差不多在130万-150万元左右。
By the end of a month, the cost of planting more than 500 mu of flowers is about 1.3 million to 1.5 million yuan.
因为冬季是鲜花市场的旺季，夏季是淡季。
Because winter is the season of flowers, summer is the low season.
李叔说，只能希望疫情尽快过去，看是否在3月8日妇女节前有好转。
He said he could only hope that the outbreak would soon be over and see if there was any improvement before March 8, the Women's Day.
。
.
据李叔反映，他们公司目前的状态是咬着牙熬，已经在筹钱以便渡过困难时期。
According to Uncle Li, his company is now gritting its teeth and is already raising money to tide it over.
当被问及能否会获得当地金融机构的贷款时，李叔坦言，银行一般不会给花农贷款，即使贷款，额度也很低，根本解决不了问题。
Asked if he would be able to get loans from local financial institutions, Mr. Li confessed that banks generally don't lend to flower farmers, and even loans are too low to solve the problem.
。
.
李叔说，熬下去只能要自救，靠自己四处借钱。
Uncle Li said he would have to save himself and borrow money on his own.
。
.
2月12日，李叔鲜花种植地所在的楚雄彝族自治州人民政府官网发文《致全州企业的一封信》。
Feb. 12, the Chu Xiong Yi Autonomous Prefectural People's Government, where Li's flowers grow, sent a letter to the enterprises of the whole state.
文中表示，为切实帮助企业降本增效，支持企业健康发展，稳定就业，坚决打赢疫情防控阻击战，共克时艰，我们共同做好：。
In order to effectively help enterprises reduce costs and increase efficiency, support the healthy development of enterprises, stabilize employment, resolutely win the battle against epidemic prevention and control, overcome difficulties, we do a good job together.
第一，切实减轻企业负担。
First, we should effectively reduce the burden on enterprises.
为维护企业职工合法权益，保障失业人员基本生活，预防失业、促进就业，各企业应按照《云南省失业保险条例》规定，到县市失业保险经办机构办理失业保险参保登记。
In order to protect the legitimate rights and interests of the workers and staff, safeguard the basic livelihood of the unemployed, prevent unemployment and promote employment, enterprises should register for unemployment insurance coverage with the unemployment insurance agencies of counties and cities in accordance with the Regulations on Unemployment Insurance of Yunnan Province.
为切实减轻企业负担，至2021年4月30日前，失业保险费率仍按工资总额的1%缴纳；第二，最大限度稳定就业岗位。
In order to effectively reduce the burden on enterprises, unemployment insurance rates will still be paid at 1 per cent of the gross wage until 30 April 2021; second, maximum stability of employment.
不裁员或少裁员的参保缴费企业要积极到县市失业保险经办机构申请稳岗返还；第三，企业参保登记、缴费等业务可延期办理；第四，给予职业培训费补贴。
Enterprises that do not reduce or reduce staff should actively apply to the county unemployment insurance agencies for the return of stable post; third, enterprises can participate in the registration of insurance, payment of fees and other business can be extended; and fourth, subsidies for vocational training fees.
。
.
李叔坦言，希望可以熬到2020年冬天鲜花市场的旺季。
Li said he hoped to see the flower market through the winter of 2020.
